de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.transform.imslex

Class IMSlexConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.transform.imslex.IMSlexConverter

  • public class IMSlexConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class converts a preprocessed version of IMSlex - Subcategorization Frames (SCF) (see PhD thesis of Judith Eckle-Kohler, 1999) to Uby-LMF. This lexical resource provides SCFs of verbs, nouns and adjectives as well as some additional syntactic and semantic properties of nouns and adjectives.
    Author:
    Judith Eckle-Kohler
